The problem is more of that he's got like, what? 300 people trying to download a 6.5 gig file and he's the only one seeding. We can't get more seeds until someone else can get a full download completed, and we can't get a full download without better seeding... it's very much a catch 22. I hate to say this, but maybe DonQuiggifur should limit the number of people who can download from him, so that maybe a few may be able to get a full torrent.
